#

Pudding Jello Shots

15 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 12

Allergens:

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Description

A fun and colorful treat combining creamy pudding with sweet jello in a shot glass!

Ingredients

  • instant pudding mix: 1 box
  • jello mix: 1 box
  • water: 2 cups
  • whipped cream: Optional for topping
  • shot glasses: 12
